short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: YouTube's < & > only go so far, let's have them go to infinity.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
YouTube's player allows fast forwarding (with the > key) only up to 2x.

This extension allows you to ff to infinity in 0.5x increments.

Code is open sourced at https://github.com/fenollp/faster-playback-on-youtube
